    "created_at": "2013-10-28T22:08:56Z",
    "updated_at": "2013-10-28T22:08:56Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Just adding a note from the dev meeting: We are going ahead with this simplification, but in the opposite direction - dropping XDG as the default, preferring ~/.ipython for cross-platform consistency.\n\nCases:\n- `~/.ipython` and `XDG/ipython` both found: warn that XDG is ignored\n- only `XDG/ipython` found: move to ~/.ipython, warn about deprecation\n"
